						<h2 class="pagetitle">Function Reference/get children</h2>
									<!-- start content -->
				<p class="LanguageLinks" style="border:1px solid #CCCCCC; line-height:1.5; text-align:left; color:#333333; font-size:90%; padding:10px;"><span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/Multilingual_Codex" title="Multilingual Codex" class="mw-redirect">Languages</a>:</span> 
<strong class="selflink">English</strong> • 
<a href="http://wpdocs.sourceforge.jp/%E9%96%A2%E6%95%B0%E3%83%AA%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%83%AC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9/get_children" class="external text" title="http://wpdocs.sourceforge.jp/%E9%96%A2%E6%95%B0%E3%83%AA%E3%83%95%E3%82%A1%E3%83%AC%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9/get_children">日本語</a> • 
<a href="/pt-br:Refer%C3%AAncia_de_Fun%C3%A7%C3%A3o/get_children" title="pt-br:Referência de Função/get children" class="mw-redirect">Português do Brasil</a> • 

<a href="/%D0%A1%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%BE%D1%87%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA_%D0%BF%D0%BE_%D1%84%D1%83%D0%BD%D0%BA%D1%86%D0%B8%D1%8F%D0%BC/get_children" title="Справочник по функциям/get children">Русский</a> • 

 <small>(<a href="/Multilingual_Codex#Language_Cross_Reference" title="Multilingual Codex" class="mw-redirect">Add your language</a>)</small>
</p>
